column5: Hey, goin up to a park off this lake for the weekend and could rent a boat to go dip a line. Was wondering if anyone on here fishes the lake or if its worthwhile to give it a try>  Website says rainbows, lakers and smallies but was wondering if anyone had firsthand experience  Tight lines  Tyler
I did okay for smallies. It was a while ago I think it was off of pencil weeds.
